otherwise returns an error code.\n\n## Remarks\n\nThis is a static method.\n\n## Requirements\n------------\n>**MOF:** DscCore.mof\n\n>**Namespace**: Root\\Microsoft\\Windows\\DesiredStateConfiguration\n\n\n## See also\n\n\n[**MSFT_DSCLocalConfigurationManager**](msft-dsclocalconfigurationmanager.md)\n\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n"}